This program is only intended to run with the question files provided with the book series LPI-1 and LPI-2 of Harald Maa√üen in German. It does not come with any questions.
Please copy the lpicX.xml files from the trainers CD to your android device. The X stands for the file number. Then select this file in the file open dialog. Please install the OI file manager from
the Android Play Store.

Usage

Select the questions using the sliders. Then press the start button.

The refresh symbol in the top bar solves all questions and marks if correctly or wrongly answered.

Navigate between answers by left and right swiping or by the arrows. The Looking glass icon in the bottom bar solves the current question.

Settings

One can change the theme and text size in the settings. Also one can enable shuffling of questions.

